54static int input_kex_dh_gex_group(int, u_int32_t, struct ssh *);
55static int input_kex_dh_gex_reply(int, u_int32_t, struct ssh *);
56
57int
58kexgex_client(struct ssh *ssh)
59{
60 struct kex *kex = ssh->kex;
61 int r;
62 u_int nbits;
63
64 nbits = dh_estimate(kex->dh_need * 8);
65
66 kex->min = DH_GRP_MIN;
67 kex->max = DH_GRP_MAX;
68 kex->nbits = nbits;
69 if (datafellows & SSH_BUG_DHGEX_LARGE)
70 kex->nbits = MINIMUM(kex->nbits, 4096);
71 /* New GEX request */
72 if ((r = sshpkt_start(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_REQUEST)) != 0 ||
73 (r = sshpkt_put_u32(ssh, kex->min)) != 0 ||
74 (r = sshpkt_put_u32(ssh, kex->nbits)) != 0 ||
75 (r = sshpkt_put_u32(ssh, kex->max)) != 0 ||
76 (r = sshpkt_send(ssh)) != 0)
77 goto out;
78 debug("SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_REQUEST(%u<%u<%u) sent",
79 kex->min, kex->nbits, kex->max);
80#ifdef DEBUG_KEXDH
81 fprintf(stderr, "\nmin = %d, nbits = %d, max = %d\n",
82 kex->min, kex->nbits, kex->max);
83#endif
84 ssh_dispatch_set(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_GROUP,
85 &input_kex_dh_gex_group);
86 r = 0;
87 out:
88 return r;
89}
90
91static int
92input_kex_dh_gex_group(int type, u_int32_t seq, struct ssh *ssh)
93{
94 struct kex *kex = ssh->kex;
95 BIGNUM *p = NULL, *g = NULL;
96 const BIGNUM *pub_key;
97 int r, bits;
98
99 debug("got SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_GROUP");
100
101 if ((r = sshpkt_get_bignum2(ssh, &p)) != 0 ||
102 (r = sshpkt_get_bignum2(ssh, &g)) != 0 ||
103 (r = sshpkt_get_end(ssh)) != 0)
104 goto out;
105 if ((bits = BN_num_bits(p)) < 0 ||
106 (u_int)bits < kex->min || (u_int)bits > kex->max) {
107 r = SSH_ERR_DH_GEX_OUT_OF_RANGE;
108 goto out;
109 }
110 if ((kex->dh = dh_new_group(g, p)) == NULL) {
111 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
112 goto out;
113 }
114 p = g = NULL; /* belong to kex->dh now */
115
116 /* generate and send 'e', client DH public key */
117 if ((r = dh_gen_key(kex->dh, kex->we_need * 8)) != 0)
118 goto out;
119 DH_get0_key(kex->dh, &pub_key, NULL);
120 if ((r = sshpkt_start(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_INIT)) != 0 ||
121 (r = sshpkt_put_bignum2(ssh, pub_key)) != 0 ||
122 (r = sshpkt_send(ssh)) != 0)
123 goto out;
124 debug("SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_INIT sent");
125#ifdef DEBUG_KEXDH
126 DHparams_print_fp(stderr, kex->dh);
127 fprintf(stderr, "pub= ");
128 BN_print_fp(stderr, pub_key);
129 fprintf(stderr, "\n");
130#endif
131 ssh_dispatch_set(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_GROUP, NULL);
132 ssh_dispatch_set(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_REPLY, &input_kex_dh_gex_reply);
133 r = 0;
134out:
135 BN_clear_free(p);
136 BN_clear_free(g);
137 return r;
138}
139
140static int
141input_kex_dh_gex_reply(int type, u_int32_t seq, struct ssh *ssh)
142{
143 struct kex *kex = ssh->kex;
144 BIGNUM *dh_server_pub = NULL;
145 const BIGNUM *pub_key, *dh_p, *dh_g;
146 struct sshbuf *shared_secret = NULL;
147 struct sshbuf *tmp = NULL, *server_host_key_blob = NULL;
148 struct sshkey *server_host_key = NULL;
149 u_char *signature = NULL;
150 u_char hash[SSH_DIGEST_MAX_LENGTH];
151 size_t slen, hashlen;
152 int r;
153
154 debug("got SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_REPLY");
155 /* key, cert */
156 if ((r = sshpkt_getb_froms(ssh, &server_host_key_blob)) != 0)
157 goto out;
158 /* sshkey_fromb() consumes its buffer, so make a copy */
159 if ((tmp = sshbuf_fromb(server_host_key_blob)) == NULL) {
160 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
161 goto out;
162 }
163 if ((r = sshkey_fromb(tmp, &server_host_key)) != 0 ||
164 (r = kex_verify_host_key(ssh, server_host_key)) != 0)
165 goto out;
166 /* DH parameter f, server public DH key, signed H */
167 if ((r = sshpkt_get_bignum2(ssh, &dh_server_pub)) != 0 ||
168 (r = sshpkt_get_string(ssh, &signature, &slen)) != 0 ||
169 (r = sshpkt_get_end(ssh)) != 0)
170 goto out;
171 if ((shared_secret = sshbuf_new()) == NULL) {
172 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
173 goto out;
174 }
175 if ((r = kex_dh_compute_key(kex, dh_server_pub, shared_secret)) != 0)
176 goto out;
177 if (ssh->compat & SSH_OLD_DHGEX)
178 kex->min = kex->max = -1;
179
180 /* calc and verify H */
181 DH_get0_key(kex->dh, &pub_key, NULL);
182 DH_get0_pqg(kex->dh, &dh_p, NULL, &dh_g);
183 hashlen = sizeof(hash);
184 if ((r = kexgex_hash(
185 kex->hash_alg,
186 kex->client_version,
187 kex->server_version,
188 kex->my,
189 kex->peer,
190 server_host_key_blob,
191 kex->min, kex->nbits, kex->max,
192 dh_p, dh_g,
193 pub_key,
194 dh_server_pub,
195 sshbuf_ptr(shared_secret), sshbuf_len(shared_secret),
196 hash, &hashlen)) != 0)
197 goto out;
198
199 if ((r = sshkey_verify(server_host_key, signature, slen, hash,
200 hashlen, kex->hostkey_alg, ssh->compat)) != 0)
201 goto out;
202
203 if ((r = kex_derive_keys(ssh, hash, hashlen, shared_secret)) == 0)
204 r = kex_send_newkeys(ssh);
205 out:
206 explicit_bzero(hash, sizeof(hash));
207 DH_free(kex->dh);
208 kex->dh = NULL;
209 BN_clear_free(dh_server_pub);
210 sshbuf_free(shared_secret);
211 sshkey_free(server_host_key);
212 sshbuf_free(tmp);
213 sshbuf_free(server_host_key_blob);
214 free(signature);
215 return r;
216}
